{"tid":2438601,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"UA戲院現金券「絕版」掀炒風 賣家「回憶」做噱頭炒貴10倍","createTime":"2021-03-08T15:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T10:52:59.000Z","uid":66271,"like":25,"dislike":211,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"28f9792d82c5a799a89a3ed3e7413ad0eef23429","tid":2438601,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"已營運36年的UA Cinemas（娛藝院線）今日（8日）宣布全線停業，令一眾影迷感到十分不捨及可惜。香港向來炒風盛行，有手持UA戲院現金券的市民眼見機不可失，竟在網上二手拍賣平台炒賣UA戲院現金券，其中有人更叫價貴足10倍。<br />\n<br />\n有不少賣家今日在UA戲院宣布結業後，紛紛在二手拍賣平台「Carousell」上放售UA戲院現金券。未知是否擔心手中現金券變成「廢紙」欲「止蝕」，有賣家以「良心價」10元放售價值50元的現金券。<br />\n<br />\n不過，亦有賣家乘機炒貴UA戲院現金券，以貴5倍或以上的價格放售，其中有人以500元放售2020年12月31日到期、貌似在銀包內放了良久、十分殘舊的50元現金券，更標明是「絕版」。<br />\n<br />\n同時，亦有賣家以每張550元的價格，放售分別於今年3月31日、8月31日、9月30日到期的50元現金券，更標明：<br />\n<br />\n「擁有36年歷史UA戲院於3月8日正式結業，其代用券已成永久珍藏，實屬香港人集體回憶。」<br />\n<br />\n而最誇張的是，有賣家以貴10倍的價錢，即每張1,000元，放售2張於今年12月31日到期的100元現金券。而在貨品描述中，賣家標明：<br />\n<br />\n「UA紀念品，K11特別版，極具珍藏價值，36年結業執笠回憶，香港人精神集體回憶。」<br />\n除了有人放售UA戲院現金券外，亦有賣家乘機炒賣上世紀90年代起的UA戲院電影票尾，售價為200元。對於上述炒賣行為，不少網民認為「有價冇市」，賣家打算無本生利的如意算盤或未能打響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2895000/2895623/ua08032021114_censored_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2895000%2F2895623%2Fua08032021114_censored_600.jpg&h=52c11255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2895000/2895623/ua08032021123_censored_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2895000%2F2895623%2Fua08032021123_censored_600.jpg&h=025e394d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2895000/2895623/ua08032021120_censored_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2895000%2F2895623%2Fua08032021120_censored_600.jpg&h=7940bbae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8f773fb11d7c16cb834e1c186877581e9fde05a","tid":2438601,"uid":73241,"like":233,"dislike":0,"score":233,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T15:14:17.000Z","msg":"咁都有得炒"},{"pid":"f0ac38fc9816cea18cd0e0902eff36aec0abea2b","tid":2438601,"uid":52727,"like":275,"dislike":0,"score":275,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"根本無人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13bb720b1f48b13c5e78cb22690d466b0b18647","tid":2438601,"uid":76747,"like":172,"dislike":2,"score":170,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T15:19:58.000Z","msg":"香港人剩識炒炒賣賣<br />\n無講錯"},{"pid":"83eaf0418188e27dd1b52cf2edb04da429877695","tid":2438601,"uid":40397,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T15:21:15.000Z","msg":"UA 票尾我都有好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2865d2ea3b81c62649d3c19cac9d3302a7138e","tid":2438601,"uid":3172,"like":127,"dislike":0,"score":127,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T15:23:55.000Z","msg":"carousell係多on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0f5ede83c8d3770f81d89431e35f93dac528f2","tid":2438601,"uid":241399,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T15:24:45.000Z","msg":"香港大把人儲票尾啦<br />\n你話最尾一日最尾一場<br />\n我都仲接受到"},{"pid":"871efcf71d99e4427bb872c15ac212f956edd382","tid":2438601,"uid":66271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"83eaf0418188e27dd1b52cf2edb04da429877695","tid":2438601,"uid":40397,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T15:21:15.000Z","msg":"UA 票尾我都有好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T15:24:46.000Z","msg":"fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f02d1474d8a062