覺得有價值你吹得人漲咩<br />\n可能人地想紀念忘妻<br />\n何必要做判官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T16:29:34.000Z","msg":"供應問題 真正想要黎做紀念既人有幾多 <br />\n係多既就係d人開post求飛 <br />\n而唔係一黎就大把人post張廢紙鳩炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申： 覺得賣飛既有佢既自由 無話岩定錯 只不過表現到香港人真係好樣衰 有咩災難財可以發既 港人同胞實做第一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T01:12:06.000Z","msg":"有啲收藏品係少供應少需求根本無市場價<br />\n<br />\n但爛到張廢紙咁真係收收皮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ac07de0e1a19115eb40312c8a6dd05b61f9645","tid":2438601,"uid":240518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T01:12:10.000Z","msg":"乜柒都香港人精神回憶"},{"pid":"b824b9d28acad11d576e03aac8672adde203e713","tid":2438601,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T01:17:58.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792a4793ac71a39b320b0c008277cb99b384dbfb","tid":2438601,"uid":162567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"28f9792d82c5a799a89a3ed3e7413ad0eef23429","tid":2438601,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"已營運36年的UA Cinemas（娛藝院線）今日（8日）宣布全線停業，令一眾影迷感到十分不捨及可惜。香港向來炒風盛行，有手持UA戲院現金券的市民眼見機不可失，竟在網上二手拍賣平台炒賣UA戲院現金券，其中有人更叫價貴足10倍。<br />\n<br />\n有不少賣家今日在UA戲院宣布結業後，紛紛在二手拍賣平台「Carousell」上放售UA戲院現金券。未知是否擔心手中現金券變成「廢紙」欲「止蝕」，有賣家以「良心價」10元放售價值50元的現金券。<br />\n<br />\n不過，亦有賣家乘機炒貴UA戲院現金券，以貴5倍或以上的價格放售，其中有人以500元放售2020年12月31日到期、貌似在銀包內放了良久、十分殘舊的50元現金券，更標明是「絕版」。<br />\n<br />\n同時，亦有賣家以每張550元的價格，放售分別於今年3月31日、8月31日、9月30日到期的50元現金券，更標明：<br />\n<br />\n「擁有36年歷史UA戲院於3月8日正式結業，其代用券已成永久珍藏，實屬香港人集體回憶。」<br />\n<br />\n而最誇張的是，有賣家以貴10倍的價錢，即每張1,000元，放售2張於今年12月31日到期的100元現金券。而在貨品描述中，賣家標明：<br />\n<br />\n「UA紀念品，K11特別版，極具珍藏價值，36年結業執笠回憶，香港人精神集體回憶。」<br />\n除了有人放售UA戲院現金券外，亦有賣家乘機炒賣上世紀90年代起的UA戲院電影票尾，售價為200元。對於上述炒賣行為，不少網民認為「有價冇市」，賣家打算無本生利的如意算盤或未能打響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2895000/2895623/ua08032021114_censored_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2895000%2F2895623%2Fua08032021114_censored_600.jpg&h=52c11255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2895000/2895623/ua08032021123_censored_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2895000%2F2895623%2Fua08032021123_censored_600.jpg&h=025e394d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2895000/2895623/ua08032021120_censored_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2895000%2F2895623%2Fua08032021120_censored_600.jpg&h=7940bbae&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T01:19:14.000Z","msg":"on9，唔係話ua  垃圾，而係啲人揸住冇價值既垃圾當寶賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ba5f217d02693a36f481cc71617a407314dcb1","tid":2438601,"uid":90660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T02:54:17.000Z","msg":"屌你老母炒埋你老母條閪毛睇下有冇人要死仆街炒狗"},{"pid":"abc0e7702fd64a420b529a6251d6ebd4ef91c965","tid":2438601,"uid":86109,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd41f7b271d28c3b6088beb9a995cafd09e28a9d","tid":2438601,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"f13bb720b1f48b13c5e78cb22690d466b0b18647","tid":2438601,"uid":76747,"like":172,"dislike":2,"score":170,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T15:19:58.000Z","msg":"香港人剩識炒炒賣賣<br />\n無講錯"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T15:39:31.000Z","msg":"ELON MUSK 首富都要炒BTC啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T06:14:57.000Z","